Package: epistack
Title: heatMap of expression profiles
Version: 0.1.1
Authors@R: 
    c(
    person("SACI", "Safia", email = "safiasaci1995@gmail.com", role = "cre"),
    person("DEVAILLY", "Guillaume",
    email = "guillaume.devailly@inrae.fr", role = "aut"))
Description: Starting from a GRanges type file, this package is used to:
    Resize the expression matrix for a better display of heatMaps.
    Sort the expression profiles.
    Generate 04 type of plots, in order to visualize the differences between
    the profiles of expression in all our data samples.
